{"tid":44241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[當年今日] 1941年12月18日  怡和大班指揮曉士兵團抵抗日軍","createTime":"2016-12-18T06:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T13:45:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"357a7d748438ccd909170df4f5dda9b4d31fc95c","tid":44241,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3b1yBj7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3b1yBj7.jpg&h=3a4f2a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【香港保衛戰當年今日】1941年12月18日<br />\n<br />\n早上7時30分，日軍軍砲兵隊及師團右砲兵隊砲擊太古及筲箕灣，同時空襲港督府及摩星嶺。北角油庫被砲彈誤中起火，連同寶馬角的大火，濃煙隨東北風飄，形成煙幕，影響守軍視野。下午6時，筲箕灣橡膠廠及寶馬角油漆廠因砲擊起火，煙霧更濃。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣英皇道因砲擊而滿佈車輛殘骸，北岸交通隨後完全癱瘓。先前在缺糧下在九龍山脊行軍至魔鬼山防衛，如今守備港島東北的印度拉吉普營（5/7th Rajput Regiment，1825年建立，1937年來港）多次被切斷通訊，大量探射燈失靈。傍晚6時半，日軍發動登陸前掩護砲擊，目標是登陸地點一帶的守軍設施及陣地。<br />\n<br />\n晚上7時，日軍開始登艦。7時10分，日軍砲擊目標轉為內陸地區。7時20分，日軍啟航出發。同時，太古船塢被擊中起火。日軍預定的登陸地點，均被大火照亮，有利搶灘。駐守的拉吉普營命令各機槍堡及陣地向接近岸邊的日軍開火，但不夠時間消滅所有敵軍。<br />\n<br />\n晚上8時15分至28分，在砲火彈幕有序掩護下，日軍第230聯隊、第228聯隊及第229聯隊由西至東，先後於北角、太古及愛秩序灣登陸。目睹三發象徵成功登陸的紅色照明彈在黑夜輝映後，第23軍司令酒井隆中將與第38師團長佐野忠義中將在司令部舉杯祝酒。<br />\n<br />\n在缺乏中央指揮下，拉吉普營各連頑抗日軍。第230聯隊受到在北角發電廠的D連及曉士兵團的抵抗而無法進入英皇道。第228聯隊第2大隊與與C連在太古船塢進行白刃戰。第229聯隊第3大隊擊潰了需要休整的A連。<br />\n<br />\n約1小時後，日軍第二波部隊登陸，拉吉普營繼續對抗數量6倍於己的敵軍。東旅旅長華里士知悉日軍登陸後，下令集中猛轟東北岸。在印軍猛烈砲火下，日軍三個聯隊未能按照原訂計劃進攻，各自向東、南、西方盲進。<br />\n<br />\n西旅旅長羅遜除派遺米杜息士營（1st Bn., The Middlesex Regiment，1881年成立，因其先驅第57步兵團指揮官在1811年半島戰爭中，屢為法軍受傷仍命軍團死戰而被稱為&quot;Die-hards&quot;；屬機關槍營，1937年來港）第16排增援北角，亦下令「機動縱隊」佔據向西俯轍黃泥涌峽、向南遙指淺水灣的渣甸山及山脊地段。午夜時份，拉吉普營終告不支，羅遜命其營部後撤至大風拗附近。"},{"pid":"6cacdacd92e3daae2947e92d006e9bfd42b87f30","tid":44241,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"－曉士兵團簡介－<br />\n<br />\n兵團由一群年過55歳英藉商人及來自盟國和中立國的人士組成，由怡和大班百德新少校（Major J. J. Paterson）指揮。成員有36名，其中有22名港燈僱員、8名自由法軍成員、及社會名流如賽馬會秘書及77歳的香港會所秘書德輔男爵。<br />\n<br />\n18日下午，百德新少校與拉吉普營營長見面，均預計持續的砲火及濃煙有利日軍晚間登陸。曉士兵團隨後與D連失去聯絡，獲米杜息士營官兵增援。翌日，曉士兵團派遣支隊摧毀了位於砲臺山的日軍速砲小隊陣地，擊斃其指揮官的兩名少尉。<br />\n<br />\n－英軍港島防禦計劃－<br />\n<br />\n英軍將港島分為4個防禦地區（地圖粗線分界），各防禦地區設步槍戰鬥負責地區（號碼方格為機槍堡）、輕機槍分隊部署地區（橫間地段）及多部署在山脊的義勇軍軍隊部署地區（交差間地段）。<br />\n<br />\n各防禦地區更分為吸收進攻、令守軍有時間準備反攻的「前進地區」及集中兵力抵抗的「主防禦地區」（地圖虛線分界）。<br />\n<br />\n敵軍一旦登陸，守軍預備兵力將向該區兩側（地圖粗線）靠攏，堵住攻擊並伺機反擊。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n圖：登陸北角的日軍，載於1942年（昭和17年）的《海軍作戦写真記録》（<a href=\"http://goo.gl/45jP7C）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F45jP7C%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=WlE0%2BH1Q2bB1Sc%2BZ6rwjmZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8d04a918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/45jP7C）。</a><br />\n<br />\nReferences:<br />\n鄺智文、蔡耀倫：《孤獨前哨：太平洋戰爭中的香港戰役》（香港：天地圖書有限公司，2013）。"},{"pid":"573b5fb35f24547cc1158f83e186b96202cb9517","tid":44241,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"－英軍港島防禦計劃－<br />\n<br />\n各防禦地區（粗線分界）<br />\n機槍堡（號碼方格）<br />\n步槍戰鬥負責地區、輕機槍分隊部署地區（橫間地段）<br />\n義勇軍軍隊部署地區（交差間地段）<br />\n前進地區與主防禦地區（虛線分界）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1d2cWcL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1d2cWcL.jpg&h=dc1d0e82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"044f53d337d08cf0df714fa49af680da691f9d28","tid":44241,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"Source:  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WatershedHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWatershedHK%2F&d=WlE0%2BH1Q2bB1Sc%2BZ6rwjmZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=619fff7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WatershedHK/</a>"},{"pid":"3baff4fed04344e5555f54d41521578d21a85816","tid":44241,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22de7811b44bac7f1ed5fef878a23b898793d0d","tid":44241,"uid":15567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 騎士精神"},{"pid":"6ca9bfc0d5fd1dc0b54ba247d1c6b02b5313a2b2","tid":44241,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7932da7de2cfea3820053730e5c6ce1b70101696","tid":44241,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:25:33.000Z","msg":"其實應該要拍套香港保衛戰<br />\n真係好傳奇嘅戰鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b4d42a29d64f960fcab46770f72baa6aa018dd","tid":44241,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"學校唔會教既歷史"},{"pid":"e7a71d1e8a88695d3f9d06aa492476bd131c27b0","tid":44241,"uid":57118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實應該要拍套香港保衛戰<br />\n真係好傳奇嘅戰鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個好好嘅題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a10c34fe2703e3334af296f80fa031a4d76249","tid":44241,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"咪再貼二戰史好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國政府透過教科書抹黑緊日本咋<br />\n<br />\n再講今日主要敵人係支那，日本係我地好朋友，有時大仁大義面前「細節野」要忽略"},{"pid":"74bcba264eae0433fd9b333ce83dd943934fc402","tid":44241,"uid":61284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實應該要拍套香港保衛戰<br />\n真係好傳奇嘅戰鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有FF過，但應該冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043ef4b1457b289b6c2cbeac0f23e45a7ddef6e7","tid":44241,"uid":21061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪再貼二戰史好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國政府透過教科書抹黑緊日本咋<br />\n<br />\n再講今日主要敵人係支那，日本係我地好朋友，有時大仁大義面前「細節野」要忽略</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母佢地保護香港而死都叫細節野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母臭西"},{"pid":"98a0cd0fc19053152f01ed79328f6127e4e31ab0","tid":44241,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咪再貼二戰史好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國政府透過教科書抹黑緊日本咋<br />\n<br />\n再講今日主要敵人係支那，日本係我地好朋友，有時大仁大義面前「細節野」要忽略</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母佢地保護香港而死都叫細節野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母臭西</blockquote><br />\non9祟日撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c0cfd7e3ce4aa0f79e81b507fb13cfaf059c27","tid":44241,"uid":38192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪再貼二戰史好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國政府透過教科書抹黑緊日本咋<br />\n<br />\n再講今日主要敵人係支那，日本係我地好朋友，有時大仁大義面前「細節野」要忽略</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n忘記香港的歷史，忘記保衛自己家園的先烈。你自己咪同共產黨一撚樣，收皮啦，戇鳩。"},{"pid":"2ca3fb820e95153cb30856973a7c6a7d8e6968b7","tid":44241,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪再貼二戰史好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國政府透過教科書抹黑緊日本咋<br />\n<br />\n再講今日主要敵人係支那，日本係我地好朋友，有時大仁大義面前「細節野」要忽略</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你試吓同班為咗保衛香港冇咗二十歲出頭嘅仔嘅爸爸媽媽講呢句嘢，我睇怕你連人哋屋企門口都出唔到 <br />\n<br />\n嗰啲臭崇日撚根本同支那人冇分別，為咗掩護某個國家連顛倒是非都在所不惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b4d907bca4b7209bd2119cdef5b2c8e0ed9cc4","tid":44241,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:51:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪再貼二戰史好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國政府透過教科書抹黑緊日本咋<br />\n<br />\n再講今日主要敵人係支那，日本係我地好朋友，有時大仁大義面前「細節野」要忽略</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9仔咪呢D囉"},{"pid":"7c543182fe45a8fefd57ee4dbb6e3eb9946ba10d","tid":44241,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿回戅鳩</span>"},{"pid":"5a5e6f0df50ee2a6efad72a3a874612851bcc9eb","tid":44241,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿回戅鳩</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支持分享，正確認識"},{"pid":"ae884b3e0a441f98a9f637663327b9aeb7fbb3be","tid":44241,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}